	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S1/The_protagonist_frowns.mp3" volume="1.0"]
	The Protagonist frowns, processing the information.
	Conrad: So it was either someone with inside knowledge, or...
	Mark: Or someone who figured it out. But here's the worst part.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S1/Mark_lowers_his_voice.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	audio music -
	Mark lowers his voice.
